content: Artemis is a domestic shorthair cat with sleek black fur and striking green eyes
Artemis was adopted from a local shelter on March 15, 2022
Artemis loves to nap on sunny window sills, especially in the afternoon
Artemis is 3 years old and celebrates her birthday in June
Artemis has a peculiar habit of drinking water from running faucets instead of her bowl
Artemis is afraid of thunderstorms and hides under the bed when it rains
Artemis's favorite treat is tuna-flavored crunchy treats
Artemis knows how to open cabinet doors with her paw to explore the kitchen
Artemis has a gentle temperament and gets along well with visitors
